	Added getConfigId() and getMaxAge() methods.

2020-08-06  Allen D. Ball  <ball@hcf.dev>

	* src/main/java/ball/upnp/ssdp/SSDPDiscoveryService.java:
	Added multicast() and send() "without delay" variant methods.

