	Added notify(BiConsumer<URI,URI>) default method.

2020-08-05  Allen D. Ball  <ball@hcf.dev>

	* src/main/java/ball/upnp/ssdp/SSDPRequest.java,
	src/main/java/ball/upnp/ssdp/SSDPResponse.java:
	Added header(String,Number) method.

	* Support UPnP 2.0 Discovery.

	* src/main/java/ball/upnp/ant/taskdefs/SSDPTask.java:
	Added support for "product" attribute (with default value).

	* src/main/java/ball/upnp/ssdp/SSDPDiscoveryCache.java:
	Changed Map entry value type to SSDPMessage.

	* src/main/java/ball/upnp/ssdp/SSDPMessage.java:
	Added getExpiration() method to interface and provided
	implementations in concrete subclasses.

	* src/main/java/ball/upnp/ssdp/SSDPDiscoveryService.java:
	Added product parameter to sole constructor.  Added getUserAgent()
	and msearch(int,URI) methods.

2020-07-31  Allen D. Ball  <ball@hcf.dev>

	* src/main/java/ball/upnp/SSDP.java:
	Added getUSNMap() and getUSN(URI) interface methods and static
	matches(URI,URI) and matches(URI) methods to compare NT to STs.
	Added the corresponding implementations in the class hierarchy.

